'''Tin''' '''[[Timo]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: hair) waa dun yariis ah oo ka soo baxda maqaarka [[jidh]]ka [[dad]]ka iyo in badan oo [[xoolo|xoolaha]] iyo [[xayawaan]]ka ka mid ah.<ref>"maqaarka [[jidh]]ka [[dad]]ka iyo in badan oo [[xoolo|xoolaha]]"</ref>
Timaha xoolaha iyo xayawaanka waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[dhogor]].<ref>"[[dhogor]]"</ref> Dhogortu waa tin dheer oo aad u awood badan taasi oo inta badan u samaysan qaab wareegsan ama duuduuban. 

Guud ahaan timuhu waxay ka samaysan yihiin borotiin loo yaqaano "keratin". 
Xayawaano badan oo [[naasley]] ah ma lahan wax dhogor ah, kuwaas waxaa ka mid ah [[maroodi]]ga iyo [[nibiri]]ga.<ref>"borotiin loo yaqaano "keratin""</ref><ref>"[[naasley]] ah ma lahan wax dhogor ah, kuwaas waxaa ka mid ah [[maroodi]]ga iyo [[nibiri]]ga."</ref> 

=Faa'iidada Timaha=
[[File:Just_one_lion.jpg|thumb|[[Aar]]ku wuxuu leeyahay dhogor badan taasi oo u eekaysiisa mid wayn.]]

Timuhu shaqo badan ayay u hayaan jidhka [[noole|noolaha]], waxaana ka mid ah:

::*ineey ka difaacaan [[ileys]]ka waxyeelada u ah jidhka. 
::*ineey sii yaan [[kul]] iyo [[qaboow]] jidhka. 
::*waxay difaac u yihiin daloolo jidhku ka soo bixiyo dhididka iyo qashinka saa'idka ah. 
::*xayawaano badan dhogorta ayaa ka difaacda in [[biyo|biyaha]] [[roob]]ku gaadhaan jidhkooda. 
::*dhogortu waxay ka dhigtaa xayawaanada qaarkood mid aad u wayn. 

=Timaha Dadka=
[[File:Mark_Twain-Shirtless-ca1883.jpg|thumb|Timuhu waxay ka soo baxaan meelo badan oo jidhka ah.]]

[[Dad]]ku waxay leeyihiin timo badan oo ka soo baxa meelo kala duwan oo [[jidh]]ka ah. Inta ugu badan timuhu waxay ka soo baxaan [[madax]]a, [[weji]]ga [[lab]]ka (timaha wejiga ka soo baxa waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[gadh]] iyo [[shaarbo]]),<ref>"[[madax]]a, [[weji]]ga [[lab]]ka (timaha wejiga ka soo baxa waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[gadh]] iyo [[shaarbo]])"</ref> [[laab]]ta, [[lug]]aha iyo gacmaha.<ref>"[[laab]]ta, [[lug]]aha iyo gacmaha"</ref> 

Bulshooyinka [[duni]]ku way ku kala duwan yihiin [[midab]]ka iyo [[tiro|tirada]] timaha; [[Aasiya]]anka iyo dadka dega [[Ameerika|Ameerikooyinka]]<ref>"[[Aasiya]]anka iyo dadka dega [[Ameerika|Ameerikooyinka]]"</ref> ayaa ugu yar timaha ka soo baxa jidhka, waxaana ugu badan dadka reer [[Yurub]]. 

=Midabka Timaha=

Midabka timaha dabiiciga ah waxaa qofku ka dhaxlaa waalidka, kuwaasi oo ku dhex jira "jiiniska" (genes). Waxaa jira noocyo badan oo midabka timaha dadka ah. Kuwaas waxaa ka mid ah: midabka madoowga ah, timaha midabka cas, timaha midabka cowlan leh iyo inta u dhexaysa kuwaas. 

